commit.message:
hash-traits.h (ggc_hasher::remove): Take a reference parameter.

gcc/
	* hash-traits.h (ggc_hasher::remove): Take a reference parameter.
	(ggc_hasher::ggc_mx): Likewise.
	(ggc_cache_hasher): Inherit from ggc_hasher.  Remove definitions
	that duplicate ggc_hasher ones.
